channel.title: ~~ ProjectCorrupt 317 ~~
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i90.photobucket.com/albums/k243/cdv721/ProjectCorrupt.jpg[/img][/center] [center]317 delta based server. I want to make a 100% F2p server with the exceptions of a FEW items such as GS's, and Dragon platelegs. Heres my progress so far:
[/center] Economy 80% [complete until perfect] Donation button linked to game 100%[Flawless aswell] Dueling 70% [Gotta fix the forfeiting] 9 Fully working quests 90% [Configure them to f2p] Perfect Combat 80% [attacking sometimes stops] Perfect Magics 80% [spell animation needs to be added] Animated Npc's 30% [Only a few are fully animated] Tutorial Island 70% [Npc dialogue needed + requirements to tele.] Fair NPC drops 90% [Finish when NPC's spawned] Strength Minigame 80% [Points given and shop made for it just gotta clean it up.] Fair Exp Rate 100% [105exp per hit] All GodSwords 90% [Sara special is messy] Working Primitive Clan Chat 100% [Old school clan chat.] 100% Working Wilderness [All working areas and levels] /Ill add more as i progress
Obviously I just started this server. Im looking for anyone who is willing to become co-owner of Projectcorrupt and help me code the server.
Credits: Delta 80% for base Me 20% for edits
